Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:58.77,jp-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}鮮やかに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:03.61,jp-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}結んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:10.57,jp-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}この気持ちごと離れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:13.48,jp-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}固く固く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:22.71,jp-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}ひと結び　人を結んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:29.17,jp-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}期待の止まない先へ明日へ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:17.73,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}无言之间 玩着翻花绳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:26.05,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}「手真巧」 试着露出一个微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:33.22,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}我唯一擅长的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:41.66,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}隐藏心声 不让任何人察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:46.06,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}但是那套在手上的美丽圆环
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:49.83,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}用那微弱的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:56.61,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}拉近了我们之间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:58.77,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}巧妙地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:03.61,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}联系起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:10.57,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}连同这份情谊 永不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:13.48,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}牢牢地 牢牢地
